| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0375 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 33a86df3-15d0-56d7-919e-f6c56fba42a6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
